Enum RequestType

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<RequestType>
      • ProtocolHandler.RequestType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<RequestType>
    public enum RequestType
extends java.lang.Enum<RequestType>
    A RequestType is an enumeration of all possible requests that can come from the client.
